{"tid":818364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指做家務是煉獄 美14歲少年焗死兩弟妹「我是拯救佢地」","createTime":"2018-09-14T05:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T10:30:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cf21ae897ac11f5b275518419c0010ff8f1e946b","tid":818364,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CpbmxqZvS0eYXQavJh1uOg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2018-09/50fbb080-b7d1-11e8-b6df-42eb14986824\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FCpbmxqZvS0eYXQavJh1uOg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2018-09%2F50fbb080-b7d1-11e8-b6df-42eb14986824&h=1bcda0de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】美國印第安納州一名14歲少年，去年在家中先後以毛巾及被子將其分別11個月大及23個月大的弟妹活生生焗死，被控以兩項謀殺罪。少年稱，因為不想弟妹長大後，要好似他一樣生活在家務的「煉獄」中，於是「在火焰中救他們出來」。涉案少年現被拘留在兒童院，需接受精神診斷。<br />\n<br />\n當地檢察官赫特爾（Richard Hertel）周三（12日）表示，警方在上周將少年拘捕，當時他只得13歲，被控於去年5月，殺害其23個月大的繼妹麥卡特尼（Desiree McCartney），繼而在7月殺害其11個月大的繼弟里茨（Nathaniel Ritz）。少年受審訊時曾稱，自己曾跟神對話，他在天使幫助下，將弟妹從地獄的火焰中救出來。<br />\n<br />\n少年的祖母得悉事件真相，表示傷心，更問他為何要殺人，他居然說「因不想弟妹長大後像自己那樣被對待。」他形容家務是「地獄」，更向警員表示「你(有)沒看過我需要完成的家務清單」，其後，少年又辯稱「沒想過會發生這種事，沒想過傷害弟妹」。<br />\n<br />\n涉案少年另涉一宗虐貓案，他的叔叔指，少年一次因遭家中的貓抓傷，居然用力將小貓捏至內臟流出。<br />\n<br />\n涉案少年被扣留在兒童院，周一（10日）出庭受審。檢察官赫特爾直言，「我工作了19年，可以說從未見過這麼令人不安的事情。」據了解，涉案青年在青少年法庭被判刑，料在18歲即可獲釋，赫特爾質疑僅3年刑期「太少」。目前，法官仍未判定他是否有能力接受聆訊，以及應否將個案當作成人謀殺處理。"},{"pid":"fbafbce342d863bddf7eb2c9cd3d228bee932ac4","tid":818364,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f8c66825bac1270fdfbd8ca1a6365492f2618e","tid":818364,"uid":198622,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:01:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73c95a291684ef236e62adacf33ce38b1703fac6","tid":818364,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f807367a227710887bb53578e4f0dedf792c78","tid":818364,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:12:19.000Z","msg":"有時青少年/兒童殺人, 未必關家庭背景事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4879e51c9e0cef7e00e1ff772ac3ea78c72902","tid":818364,"uid":76314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:14:21.000Z","msg":"終生監禁啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043a9763faa25993c7b9eb89745f9e1ecdc9f305","tid":818364,"uid":18955,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:14:24.000Z","msg":"5月殺完人 7月仲可以再殺人？<br />\n無人發現？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde57edc16139b107f90c3583096134bec183b98","tid":818364,"uid":41524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:15:37.000Z","msg":"我就是正義!!"},{"pid":"3c1fed82ab5e0590af7619ae7c6efb4624d62f0b","tid":818364,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"043a9763faa25993c7b9eb89745f9e1ecdc9f305","tid":818364,"uid":18955,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:14:24.000Z","msg":"5月殺完人 7月仲可以再殺人？<br />\n無人發現？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952e78aac74b97d5861d8888b7e139b4f5974181","tid":818364,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:47:47.000Z","msg":"13,14歲剛好中二病發年齡...."},{"pid":"b930d75ea5d2e1f